# Peak Interval

> Peak Interval is a precision HIIT (high-intensity interval training) timer for iOS and Apple Watch. The Peak Interval blog publishes evidence-based articles on interval training, workout protocols, sports science, nutrition, and recovery to help athletes train smarter at every level.

The Peak Interval app provides customizable interval timing, saved workouts, heart rate integration with Apple Watch, image-based workout import, AI-powered coaching, and 25+ language support. The blog covers HIIT fundamentals, workout guides, specialized training for different populations and goals, advanced concepts, and case studies — all written to help athletes apply interval training intelligently.

## App
- [Peak Interval - HIIT Timer for iOS and Apple Watch](https://www.peakintervalapp.com): Advanced interval training timer with AI Coach, heart rate zones, workout history, iCloud sync, and 25+ languages.
- [Download on the App Store](https://apps.apple.com/us/app/peak-interval-hiit-timer/id6741055716): Install the iOS and Apple Watch app.
- [Privacy Policy](https://www.peakintervalapp.com/privacy): Data practices, Apple HealthKit integration, and how user information is handled.
- [Terms of Service](https://www.peakintervalapp.com/terms): Conditions of use for the app and website.
- [Contact](https://www.peakintervalapp.com/contact): Support, feedback, and partnership inquiries.

